{"tid":824213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日係天災 今日係人禍","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T03:50:00.000Z","uid":81309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea21003888197daca03074069da31f0363a1ef45","tid":824213,"uid":81309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/觀塘有途人被塌樹壓住半身-142281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E6%9C%89%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%A1%8C%E6%A8%B9%E5%A3%93%E4%BD%8F%E5%8D%8A%E8%BA%AB-142281&d=qhK5bDgE7dGZbE5TZpbcsJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a514e95d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/觀塘有途人被塌樹壓住半身-142281</a><br />\n<br />\n早上約10時35分，觀塘翠屏南邨翠榮樓對開，有途人被塌下大樹壓住，塌樹範圍擋住兩條行車線。其他途人見狀報警救助。現場消息指，被壓途人沒有反應。<br />\n<br />\n已經唔知講咩好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭車出去見到周圍都係塌樹，<br />\n竟然仲大把人要等車行馬路返工<br />\n<br />\n巴士地鐵都停、大學停工停課，比哂signal都係堅持唔停工<br />\n<br />\n交通近乎癱瘓，大把工人趕住為你搶修呢樣個樣，而家有人塌樹壓親特首竟然趕住去致辭，急急腳跑走<br />\n<br />\n係咪香港人條命已經唔值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地到底為咩要為呢個社會賣命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}